<span id="freeTextContainer13849514204168080172">This is a beautiful, poetic story like nothing I’ve read before.<br/><br/>It took a little bit of getting used to the style of writing. Incredibly poetic! But, once I got used to that, it flowed. There is a wonderful story there that carries you away.<br/><br/>It is interspersed with poems. One of which I loved! It starts:<br/><br/>I am your child who’s just been born<br/><br/>You hold me true in loving hands<br/><br/>I am your love’s embodiment<br/><br/>You love me more than love itself<br/><br/>It goes on from there but you’ll have to buy the book to read the re</span>
  <span id="freeText13849514204168080172" style="display:none">This is a beautiful, poetic story like nothing I’ve read before.<br /><br />It took a little bit of getting used to the style of writing. Incredibly poetic! But, once I got used to that, it flowed. There is a wonderful story there that carries you away.<br /><br />It is interspersed with poems. One of which I loved! It starts:<br /><br />I am your child who’s just been born<br /><br />You hold me true in loving hands<br /><br />I am your love’s embodiment<br /><br />You love me more than love itself<br /><br />It goes on from there but you’ll have to buy the book to read the rest! I wouldn’t want to give anything away.<br /><br />What I will say is that I believe every woman has a “Swift Man”. You’ll understand once you’ve read it!<br /><br />A most enjoyable book that I would recommend.</span>
